Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter's three bills passed
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bv5m
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 22 Oct 1978
President Carter's three main policy bills finally win Congress over. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.